keyFacts: The document is an email transmitting an FBI 302 report (Form FD-302).
The subject of the 302 report is an inmate named Fernandez.
The report originates from the FBI New York Field Office, Violent Crimes Task Force.
The email transmission date was August 30, 2019.
The document is part of the Epstein case files, suggesting Fernandez may have provided information relevant to the investigation.
